**StuckPoint** is built and ready. Here's what was created:

```
demo/
├── app.py           # Flask backend + Claude API integration
├── database.py      # SQLite schema, helpers, seed data
├── requirements.txt # flask, anthropic, python-dotenv
├── README.md        # Setup and walkthrough
├── stuckpoint.db    # Pre-initialized DB with 3 topics
├── templates/
│   ├── index.html   # Home page with topic picker + progress sidebar
│   ├── topic.html   # Workspace with stuck detection + chat panel
│   └── instructor.html  # Dashboard at /instructor
└── static/
    ├── style.css    # Full design system
    └── app.js       # Inactivity timer, keyword detection, chat, instructor UI
```

**To run:**
```bash
export ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=your_key
python app.py
# → http://localhost:5000
```

All 3 MVP features are implemented:
1. **Proactive stuck detection** — 45s inactivity timer + keyword matching auto-opens chat, AI sends first message
2. **Cross-session memory** — localStorage UUID, progress sidebar, session replay, prior context injection
3. **Instructor dashboard** — `/instructor` (password: `instructor2024`), urgency colors, transcript viewer, send encouragement button with 60s auto-refresh
